                            <comment id="13058265" author="roger.hui" created="Mon, 13 Apr 2015 04:49:03 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;I just realized that BridgePropertyPlaceholder won&apos;t jasypt outside or inside camelcontext. The reason it works in my example is because I have this in my camel context. &lt;br/&gt;
